{"tid":2293704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"達明一派尾場高呼「跳舞唔使拉」 明哥撐手足：香港人要堅持","createTime":"2020-11-20T12:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T12:13:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f68161ce16440dcf2a7a525df93e16c906a417","tid":2293704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/CRM3WUWNN5G4LIHMXBY676Z634/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FCRM3WUWNN5G4LIHMXBY676Z634%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=17138567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FCRM3WUWNN5G4LIHMXBY676Z634%2F&h=a478f4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/CRM3WUWNN5G4LIHMXBY676Z634/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n達明一派尾場高呼「跳舞唔使拉」<br />\n明哥撐手足：香港人要堅持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hz-YLfZo2b_CdRycSw2pjdT07nI=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P75OCYA365EEDK6ZW4TYL6334Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHz-YLfZo2b_CdRycSw2pjdT07nI%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP75OCYA365EEDK6ZW4TYL6334Y.jpg&h=70d2e022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■達明一派昨晚舉行演唱會尾場，兩人演唱《皇后大盜》後，屏幕出現手足抱頭畫面。<br />\n<br />\n達明一派在灣仔伊館舉行六場的「REPLAY LIVE演唱會」演唱會，昨晚最後一場，RubberBand的6號及泥鯭、黃偉文、俞琤、泰迪羅賓及麥浚龍等睇騷。演唱會約8時半開騷，開場時播出獨白版《世紀末顏色》，講完幾句歌詞︰「你見過我，你有冇見過佢，你見到佢。」黃耀明隨即出台講︰「仲可以見到！」為演唱會打開序幕。明哥在整場騷中，不時提醒大家要團結有夢想。<br />\n<br />\n個唱開始不久，明哥開宗明義說會唱兩隻六四前後創作的專輯，希望大家反思歌曲意義，當《天花亂墜》音樂響起全場站立，明哥即說：「跳舞唔使拉！」唱到最尾一句他問觀眾︰「我係咪應該收聲？」全場即齊叫「No！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CTaEu4-8O_8yQeIoQzN_ONHE-rk=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RT6MV3LKMBEXRFIXEEGQQMBL4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCTaEu4-8O_8yQeIoQzN_ONHE-rk%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRT6MV3LKMBEXRFIXEEGQQMBL4E.jpg&h=1ac96024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■達明一派借今次演唱會為港人打氣，明哥更指即使歌曲被下架，但信念如瘟疫蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UvnqZwQiVXFuwQov91h1W6HBU_k=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4GR7XQVRORAKBLTW66YGCC6EZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUvnqZwQiVXFuwQov91h1W6HBU_k%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4GR7XQVRORAKBLTW66YGCC6EZQ.jpg&h=bef19232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉以達唱《排名不分先後左右忠奸》，幕牆出現前國家主席楊尚昆名字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔應該失去夢<br />\n<br />\n繼前晚現場朗讀四川歌迷信後，昨晚明哥又讀出一位廣州歌迷信，內容指2007至2010年間，廣州曾有組織為自己爭取權益、發聲，可惜最終草草收場，當廣州人見到香港市民為自己訴求發聲，身同感受，要為港人打氣，鼓勵要大家「撐下去！」明哥說︰「雖然我所有歌被下架，但（信念）就似瘟疫蔓延。」唱完《愛在瘟疫蔓延時》後，明哥指疫情令大家封閉自己，他呼籲大家多些出來見，否則似歌詞「懼怕中這地夢已失去」，他說：「香港人唔應該失去夢。」<br />\n<br />\n達明唱《皇后大盜》時，背後出現戴住頭盔的手足互相輕撫的畫面，場面令人動容。之後達明唱出《天問》，明哥唱畢後提起這首歌是六四後寫︰「喺電視見到學生紥營、軍隊入城輾過啲學生場面，個人喊到飛起，感觸瞓唔到，成晚玩音樂，就寫咗呢首歌。」<br />\n<br />\n明哥又再叫香港人堅持，達哥則說︰「壞極都好，但唔可以絕望，大家要保留實力。」到唱完《你情我願》後，明哥指當年創作這首歌，是因為當時熱論英國會否給居英權港人，他又說︰「我哋唔係戀殖，而係有獨立思想。」唱完《愛彌留》後，觀眾席有人大叫「香港人」，其他人和應「加油」持續20秒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QK0bOA0QZozQ2b5EewzuUPU360U=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F3NDMPDGF5HANIVCN45MG5CTEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQK0bOA0QZozQ2b5EewzuUPU360U%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF3NDMPDGF5HANIVCN45MG5CTEM.jpg&h=9e15b216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■柳俊江與長髮女友人到場，他見到記者即彈開一個位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pKMzvNl5cn0fg7y0A6v3QGMpEBY=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E27HQ56QZZHQTNTFSPC4J4HNXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpKMzvNl5cn0fg7y0A6v3QGMpEBY%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE27HQ56QZZHQTNTFSPC4J4HNXM.jpg&h=2c640edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■俞琤（左）與麥浚龍（右）等一齊睇達明一派演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n觀眾嗌釋放12<br />\n<br />\n演唱會尾段，觀眾以光時口號代替叫encore，亦有人大叫「毌忘義士」、「釋放12」、「香港人加油」等。在觀眾叫喊聲下，達明換衫再上台唱《自由之夏》，屏幕出現「64」字眼，明哥指：「去年係荒謬嘅一年，叫口號有罪、唱歌有罪、寫書有罪、畫畫有罪、點蠟燭有罪同回憶有罪。我見到立場姐姐，令我記得去年六四事件30周年，佢入維園仲有案件喺身未審，相信好多人當日都有去維園，係咪要拉晒所有人？好多國家有限聚令，都畀人上街表達啱嘅訴求，呢個係文明同自由社會應有。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，...................................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MGqBYZVKmrQHbwmBYUF8Xew4ZH0=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QUUA6HWE25G2HMWEJN36ADINSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMGqBYZVKmrQHbwmBYUF8Xew4ZH0%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQUUA6HWE25G2HMWEJN36ADINSQ.jpg&h=414b4a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紅姑（左）與畢明（右二）前晚入場睇騷，完場後攬實明哥合照。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3w0mkZFS5YOZhephCf2lZaGgX10=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CA4OA7V5NNAEFND7SQ52WEVSJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3w0mkZFS5YOZhephCf2lZaGgX10%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCA4OA7V5NNAEFND7SQ52WEVSJQ.jpg&h=a5c5547d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨晚是達明一派演唱會尾場，有部份周邊一早已經售罄。"}]}